Package org.xbib.io.compress.lzf.util

Package that contains helper classes that can be used along with standard JDK gzip implementation (java.util.zip).

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChunkDecoderFactory
    Simple helper class used for loading ChunkDecoder implementations, based on criteria such as "fastest available".
    LZFFileInputStream
    Helper class that allows use of LZF compression even if a library requires use of FileInputStream.
    LZFFileOutputStream
    Helper class that allows use of LZF compression even if a library requires use of FileOutputStream.

Package org.xbib.io.compress.lzf.util Description

Package that contains helper classes that can be used along with standard JDK gzip implementation (java.util.zip). This is not a separate gzip implementation, but rather set of extensions and helpers classes above and beyond JDK implementation.
